description:
Simulated and experimental single cell RNA sequencing datasets analyzed&nbsp;to benchmark  biVI&nbsp; and illustrate&nbsp; biVI 's ability to infer biophysical parameters are included in  data.zip.  All data files are described in  README_data.md.  
 Parameter inference results and figures are found in  results.zip.  All results included in results.zip are described in  README_results.md.  
 &nbsp; 
 The associated project GitHub can be found at https://github.com/pachterlab/CGCCP_2023.&nbsp; 
